## BUNHS School System - Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` (local) or set these as Railway project variables.

### Database (Required - Railway MySQL Addon)
DB_HOST=your_mysql_host.railway.internal
DB_PORT=3306
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=your_mysql_password
DB_NAME=bunhs_school_db

### Railway (Auto-detected - Don't set manually)
PORT=8080
RAILWAY_ENVIRONMENT=production
RAILWAY_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
RAILWAY_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id

### Optional - App Settings
APP_ENV=production
APP_DEBUG=false
CACHE_TTL_STATS=300
CACHE_TTL_CREDENTIALS=3600

## Railway Setup Instructions:
1. Railway Dashboard → Your Project → Variables tab
2. Add each DB_* variable from your MySQL addon's connection details
3. Click "Deploy" or run `railway up`
4. View logs: Should show "mysqli" in php -m output
5. Test: Visit deployed URL → see homepage stats (confirms DB connection)
